        <section name="DataNucleus Maven Plugin">
            <p>
                <i>datanucleus-maven-plugin</i> provides a plugin for use of DataNucleus with Maven 2+.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Compile Requirement : JDK1.5+</li>
                <li>Runtime Requirement : JDK1.5+</li>
                <li>Latest version : 3.3.1</li>
                <li>Roadmap : <a href="http://issues.datanucleus.org/browse/NUCMAVEN?report=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.project:roadmap-panel" target="_blank">Via JIRA</a></li>
                <li>License : <a href="../project/license.html">Apache 2</a></li>
                <li>Source : <a href="https://github.com/datanucleus/datanucleus-maven-plugin">latest</a></li>
            </ul>

            <subsection name="Source Code">
                <p>The plugin can be checked out as follows</p>
<source>git clone https://github.com/datanucleus/datanucleus-maven-plugin.git</source>
                <br/>
            </subsection>

            <subsection name="Download">
                <p><i>DataNucleus Maven2 Plugin</i> is downloadable as following</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Releases</b> <a href="http://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/datanucleus/datanucleus-maven-plugin/" target="_blank">from Maven Central</a></li>
                    <li><b>Nightly builds</b> <a href="http://www.datanucleus.org/downloads/maven2-nightly/org/datanucleus/datanucleus-maven-plugin/" target="_blank">from Maven2 Nightly Repository</a></li>
                </ul>
                <br/>
            </subsection>

