                        <td><a href="core.html">datanucleus-core</a></td>
                        <td>3.1+</td>
                        <td>Provides logging, localisation, and other framework facilities for DataNucleus</td>
                        <td>Yes</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><a href="store.rdbms.html">datanucleus-rdbms</a></td>
